name: Evidence 989
description:
Evidence 989, is anything that you see, experience, read, or are told that causes you to believe that something is true or has really happened. MM college on bamboo. Animated with Light Tricks edited in Kinemaster.

This NFT features the music of Cut-Out “What Now” Cut-Out is a studio project by members of Pell Mell, Robert Beerman, Greg Freeman and Steve Fisk. This music is unreleased and is being used by permission.
